==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*Πέτρος / Petros / pet'-ros
*Apparently a primary word; a (piece of) rock (larger than [[λίθος]] {{GG|3037}}); as a name, [[Petrus]], an apostle: 

===Proper noun===
'''Πέτρος'''

# [[Peter]], [[rock]]. Compare {{GG|2786}}.

